00:00:07,640 --> 00:00:11,380
SPK_1: The outline and the image is starting to become more clear.

3
00:00:11,940 --> 00:00:16,840
SPK_1: This most recent conversation, we discussed the will as self.

4
00:00:17,260 --> 00:00:27,100
SPK_1: We discussed the sleight of hand where the whole self is replaced by just a piece of self, the will.

5
