SPK_1: And then we began to actually string together a bunch of the different notions.

9
00:00:41,740 --> 00:00:52,000
SPK_1: So we could actually begin to see the whole or the assemblage, the aggregate that Gnosticism puts in place of the actual wholeness that is reality.

10
00:00:52,840 --> 00:00:53,800
SPK_1: So what's next?

11
00:00:54,080 --> 00:00:58,080
SPK_0: So next is in effect the sum of the previous two.

12
00:00:58,460 --> 00:01:00,140
SPK_0: The deal and the will.

13
00:01:01,000 --> 00:01:04,540
SPK_0: What is the Gnostic deal which is offered to the will?

14
00:01:04,680 --> 00:01:07,160
SPK_0: There is many, many, many deals.

15
