SPK_1: Yes.

102
00:06:32,900 --> 00:06:33,880
SPK_1: So you have a shortcut.

103
00:06:34,500 --> 00:06:35,620
SPK_1: On the one hand, I have a shortcut.

104
00:06:35,820 --> 00:06:38,680
SPK_1: And it may be a very hard shortcut, but it's a shortcut I can take.

105
00:06:39,120 --> 00:06:40,500
SPK_1: And this is even more to the point.

106
00:06:40,800 --> 00:06:42,940
SPK_1: I can adopt a self that is not myself.

107
00:06:43,220 --> 00:06:44,420
SPK_1: This is really critical.

108
00:06:44,640 --> 00:06:44,940
SPK_1: Yes.

109
00:06:45,060 --> 00:06:50,880
SPK_1: Because the Gnostic identity is, at the end of the day, subject only to the limitations of the aspirations of the will.

110
00:06:51,320 --> 00:06:51,640
SPK_1: Yes.

111
00:06:51,840 --> 00:06:57,320
