SPK_0: Even worse thought for a Gnostic.

152
00:08:41,100 --> 00:08:52,220
SPK_0: Like, and that's a whole part if we go into it, like, because in reality, you basically experience of a name requires a certain experience of humility.

153
00:08:53,800 --> 00:08:54,720
SPK_1: Yes, quite.

154
00:08:54,840 --> 00:08:55,260
SPK_1: Yes.

155
00:08:55,900 --> 00:08:56,360
SPK_0: Yes.

156
