SPK_0: Because you are not given your own name.

157
00:08:59,660 --> 00:09:00,540
SPK_0: Neither literally.

158
00:09:00,900 --> 00:09:09,480
SPK_0: Like you received it from your parents, but even metaphysically, your whole identity, your whole unity is in a way not of you.

159
00:09:10,120 --> 00:09:11,020
SPK_0: And you feel it.

160
00:09:11,340 --> 00:09:14,620
SPK_0: There is this nudging feeling that it's not exactly of me.

161
00:09:14,680 --> 00:09:21,600
SPK_0: There is this invisible, like mystical element, which if I go in one direction kind of works.

162
00:09:21,640 --> 00:09:25,260
SPK_0: If I go in another direction, it kind of just doesn't feel like there is this nudging feeling.

163
