SPK_1: Remember your, your deepest presupposition is that the world is fundamentally broken.

171
00:09:47,000 --> 00:09:47,320
SPK_1: Yes.

172
00:09:47,360 --> 00:09:51,160
SPK_1: So that, which has happened to me as a consequence of reality itself.

173
00:09:51,280 --> 00:09:51,620
SPK_1: Yes.

