SPK_0: I want to stop the fact of being noble, the privilege, because the name has a identity, has a privilege simply in terms of being, you can say that the being has a privilege being as something is a privilege of being something, anything, whatever it is, whatever it is.

191
00:10:58,360 --> 00:10:59,980
SPK_0: So what I'm doing.

